If you thought Shona Ferguson was a big dude, think again. Ladies and gentlemen, allow me to introduce you to WWE wrestler Brock Lesnar. After posting a snap of himself on social media, Shona was shocked to learn that he was not as big a dude as he said he was. Mr Ferguson Films himself took a picture with the legendary Brock Lesnar which caused a stir on social media as they couldn't believe how much of a difference there was between him and the wrestler. He captioned the picture he took with Brock and said, “I used to think I was a big dude.” This didn't stop fans wondering how big Brock was, calling him a freak of nature, seeing that Shona was also known to be a big man. Here are some of the reactions: